imdb.plot outline: Allee-Sutton Hethcoat embarks on life coming off her title win as Miss Tennessee 2017 and making the top 10 at the Miss USA pageant. Returning back to her love of acting and hosting, Allee-Sutton shares tips, information and inspiration in this Lifestyle Reality-show format program.
